{"id":6,"category_slug":"short-stories","category_name":"Short Stories","position":3,"title":"3. My flower garden","subtitle":"","level":"A1","parts":19,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/short-stories/3-my-flower-garden.6/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/3-my-flower-garden-2019-03-15-01-07-24/0-3-my-flower-garden.mp3","transcript":"My name is Anne.\nI love flowers.\nI have a flower garden.\nMy garden is in front of my house.\nMy neighbor has a garden too.\nMy garden has different types of flowers.\nI have roses in my garden.\nI have tulips in my garden.\nI have petunias in my garden.\nMy garden has different colors.\nI plant red flowers.\nI plant orange flowers.\nI plant blue flowers.\nI plant purple flowers.\nI take care of my garden.\nI water my garden every day.\nI kill the weeds in my garden.\nI kill insects that eat my flowers.\nI love my beautiful garden.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:55:24","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"My name is Anne.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/3-my-flower-garden-2019-03-15-01-07-24/1.mp3","time_start":3.5,"time_end":5.1},{"position":2,"content":"I love flowers.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/3-my-flower-garden-2019-03-15-01-07-24/2.mp3","time_start":5.5,"time_end":7.3},{"position":3,"content":"I have a flower garden.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/3-my-flower-garden-2019-03-15-01-07-24/3.mp3","time_start":7.8,"time_end":9.6},{"position":4,"content":"My garden is in front of my house.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/3-my-flower-garden-2019-03-15-01-07-24/4.mp3","time_start":10.2,"time_end":12.7},{"position":5,"content":"My neighbor has a garden too.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/general-english/3-my-flower-garden-2019-03-15-01-07-24/5.mp3","time_start":13.3,"time_end":15.4},{"position":6,"content":